name: Dr. Budi Santoso
description: Dr. Budi Santoso is a highly experienced clinical psychologist with a focus on evidence-based therapies to help individuals cope with various mental health issues.

name: Dr. Joko Raharjo
description: Dr. Joko Raharjo specializes in counseling psychology, providing support and guidance to individuals facing challenges in their personal and professional lives.

name: Dr. Ani Kusuma
description: Dr. Ani Kusuma is a child psychologist dedicated to helping children and their families navigate through developmental and behavioral issues with a compassionate and child-friendly approach.

name: Dr. Adi Nugroho
description: Dr. Adi Nugroho specializes in sports psychology, assisting athletes in enhancing their mental resilience, focus, and overall performance for success in their respective sports.

name: Dr. Dian Sari
description: Dr. Dian Sari, a forensic psychologist, applies psychological principles to legal and criminal matters, providing expert analysis and testimony in court cases.

name: Dr. Mega Wijaya
description: Dr. Mega Wijaya focuses on educational psychology, working with students, teachers, and educational institutions to enhance learning environments and support academic success.

name: Dr. Candra Putra
description: Dr. Candra Putra specializes in health psychology, promoting holistic well-being and addressing the psychological aspects of physical health conditions.

name: Dr. Tri Wijaya
description: Dr. Tri Wijaya is a geriatric psychologist, providing support and mental health services tailored to the unique needs of older adults.

name: Dr. Anugerah Sari
description: Dr. Anugerah Sari specializes in industrial-organizational psychology, applying psychological principles to enhance workplace dynamics, employee well-being, and organizational effectiveness.

name: Dr. Wijaya Putra
description: Dr. Wijaya Putra is a neuropsychologist, specializing in the study of brain-behavior relationships and providing assessments and interventions for individuals with neurological conditions.
